d played the part of this character in a religious play."]}]}],"historicEvents":[{"id":1705185,"age":6,"year":"1106","julianDay":2125018,"title":"The Battle of Tichebray","description":"King Henry I defeated and captured his brother, Robert of Normandy, at the Battle of Tinchebray in 1106. Robert remained in captivity until his death in 1134.","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"When Pons FitzSimon was born in 1100, in Swell, Somerset, England, his father, Simon FitzPons, was 33 and his mother, Mrs Simon Fitzpons, was 29. He had at least 2 sons. He died in 1166, in Swell, Somerset, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 66."},"et":{"1100–1166":"1100–1166","1102–Male":"1102–Surnud","1135–Male":"1135–Surnud","1162–1222":"1162–1222","1068–1150":"1068–1150","1072–Female":"1072–Surnud","1106":"1106","1135":"1135","1102":"1102","1068":"1068","1222":"1222","1100":"1100","1166":"1166","1162":"1162","1150":"1150","1072":"1072","Swell, Somerset, England":"Swell, Somerset, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1100–1166":"1100–1166","1102–Male":"1102–Kuollut","1135–Male":"1135–Kuollut","1162–1222":"1162–1222","1068–1150":"1068–1150","1072–Female":"1072–Kuollut","1106":"1106","1135":"1135","1102":"1102","1068":"1068","1222":"1222","1100":"1100","1166":"1166","1162":"1162","1150":"1150","1072":"1072","Swell, Somerset, England":"Swell, Somerset, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1100–1166":"1100–1166","1102–Male":"1102–Décédé","1135–Male":"1135–Décédé","1162–1222":"1162–1222","1068–1150":"1068–1150","1072–Female":"1072–Décédée","1106":"1106","1135":"1135","1102":"1102","1068":"1068","1222":"1222","1100":"1100","1166":"1166","1162":"1162","1150":"1150","1072":"1072","Swell, Somerset, England":"Swell, Somerset, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Pons FitzSimon est né en 1100, à Swell, Somerset, Angleterre, son père, Simon FitzPons, avait 33 ans et sa mère, Mrs Simon Fitzpons, avait 29 ans. Il a eu au moins 2 fils. Il est décédé en 1166, à Swell, Somerset, Ang